      <title>台湾金融管理委员会淡化外国人出售股票行为，关注美国大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-s-fsc-says-foreign-investor-stock-sales-only-short-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高金融监管机构表示，近期海外投资者抛售股票属于“短期现象”，并不代表看跌观点，近年来外资持股呈上升趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-s-fsc-says-foreign-investor-stock-sales-only-short-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受刺激政策预期推动，中国股市创下 2 月以来最大单日涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/chinese-stocks-eye-best-day-since-april-as-stimulus-calls-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市上涨，境内基准指数创下近六个月来的最佳单日涨幅，因为市场越来越期待北京方面将提振陷入困境的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/chinese-stocks-eye-best-day-since-april-as-stimulus-calls-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 04:04:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
